WEBVTT

00:00.086 --> 00:01.889
Previously on This Is Us...

00:01.914 --> 00:03.640
Beth, I want to adopt a baby.

00:04.594 --> 00:06.967
I realize I didn't come
to New York to be in a hit play.

00:06.992 --> 00:09.131
I came to New York to win back my girl.

00:09.586 --> 00:11.753
Hello. Hey, Kevin, it's Ron Howard.

00:11.788 --> 00:14.122
I'm prepping a movie right now
that I'm gonna direct.

00:14.157 --> 00:15.624
It shoots in Los Angeles.

00:15.658 --> 00:17.281
You would be perfect.

00:17.781 --> 00:18.858
I know what I want to do.

00:18.882 --> 00:20.687
- I want to sing.
- Hmm.

00:20.884 --> 00:23.414
- Whoa! What the hell was that?
- Sorry.

00:23.439 --> 00:25.098
Don't punish her because
I crossed the line.

00:25.122 --> 00:26.831
- Hey, Bec?
- What'd you say?

00:27.624 --> 00:30.059
Hey, hey, come on. Come on.

00:30.094 --> 00:31.265
Jack!

00:31.854 --> 00:34.546
I think you should go stay
with Miguel for a while.

